                "invention-title": [
                    "Preparation method of microporous instant sodium percarbonate",
                    "一种微孔速溶型过氧碳酸钠的制备方法"
                ]
            },
            "abstract": [
                {
                    "p": "The invention provides a preparation method of microporous instant sodium percarbonate. The preparation method comprises the following steps: adding a certain amount of sodium bicarbonate into a sodium carbonate solution to prepare a saturated solution; adding a hydrogen peroxide stabilizer into the hydrogen peroxide solution and uniformly stirring; dropwise adding the solution in the step 2) into the saturated solution in the step 1), carrying out low-temperature crystallization reaction, and carrying out centrifugal treatment to obtain an intermediate product; and 3) drying the intermediate product in the step 3) at a controlled temperature to decompose the sodium bicarbonate to release carbon dioxide so as to form micropores in the sodium percarbonate particles, and finally obtaining the microporous instant sodium percarbonate product. The method has the advantages that the density of sodium percarbonate particles is reduced, the stacking density of the product is reduced, and no other substances are introduced in the reaction process, so that the prepared sodium percarbonate product can quickly release effective active oxygen during use."
                },
                {
                    "p": "本发明提供一种微孔速溶型过氧碳酸钠的制备方法，包括如下步骤：在碳酸钠溶液里加入一定量碳酸氢钠配成饱和溶液；在双氧水溶液中加入双氧水稳定剂并搅拌均匀；将步骤2）中溶液滴加到步骤1）中饱和溶液进行低温结晶反应，并进行离心处理后得到中间产品；将步骤3）中的中间产品进行控温烘干，使得碳酸氢钠分解释放二氧化碳从而在过碳酸钠颗粒内部形成微孔，最终得到微孔速溶型过氧碳酸钠产品。本发明的优点为：降低过氧碳酸钠颗粒致密度，降低产品堆积密度，反应过程中不引入其他物质，使得制成的过氧碳酸钠产品在使用时可快速释放有效活性氧。"
                }
            ]
